  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dab\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0d91\u0dc3\u0dca.\u0d91\u0dc6\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Former SF soldier Mattu who ran a brothel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Vavuniya Police say that three people, including a former Army Special Forces soldier, were arrested with 30 rounds of ammunition used for T.56 firearms and a uniform similar to an army uniform in a lodge in Thekkawatta area, Vavuniya.",
        "According to the information received by the Vavuniya police that a brothel was being run in the lodge, the police said that during a raid, an ex-army soldier, the manager of the lodge and two women engaged in prostitution were arrested.",
        "Police also mentioned that women have been engaged in prostitution in the lodge for a long time and information was revealed that the manager of the lodge and army soldiers have employed women in prostitution and obtained money.",
        "It was said that for emergency exits from the lodge, several secret exit doors had been installed in the rooms and the dogs of the police official dog department were deployed and conducted inspections.",
        "The arrested suspects are residents of Vavuniya Mamaduwa, Ataweeragollewa and Anuradhapura, aged between 40 and 30 years."
      ],
